1. Go to :
   http://www.google.com/enterprise/marketplace/viewListing?productListingId=5143210+12982233047309328439&pli=1

2. Click "Add it now"

3. Check off and enter domain name:
   [x] I accept. Continue to add this service.
   Web Address: http://[codereview].alexeypro.com

4. Click "Continue to set up URL"

5. (In other browser window) Sign in to GoDaddy -- follow instructions
   https://mya.godaddy.com/default.aspx

6. Click "I've completed these steps"

7. Access it here :
   http://codereview.alexeypro.com/

8. Download upload.py :
   http://codereview.alexeypro.com/static/upload.py

9. Modify upload-git.sh with your email and paths.

10. Update Git pre-commit hookups : 
   $ cd /code/git/my-repository
   $ /bin/sh /path/where/rietveld-upload-git-is/install-git-hooks.sh

11. That's it.


